ore do not support recent\nclaims that these alternative scenarios to CDM can survive astrophysical data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 May 2012 11:04:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Nov 2012 08:39:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
